CLIENT
================

The game client is implemented in objective-c using cocos2d-iphone Framework (LGPL), 
you can see the cocos2d-iphone homepage at <http://code.google.com/p/cocos2d-iphone/>.
In directory named "Babel" there is a file project for XCode (you need install iPhone SDK).


SERVER
================

The game server is implemented in python 2.5+, the scripts are in directory named "Net".


ABOUT DATABASE
================

Both the client and the server uses a sqlite3 database (python need a module).